{"tid":1166351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南海仲裁既結果話比我聽 中國唔會死 只會更多","createTime":"2019-05-22T11:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T03:20:13.000Z","uid":98232,"like":11,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f0bcb7eca1ecc64794e29ad7ed94cf8412b1ac74","tid":1166351,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:15:58.000Z","msg":"當年南海仲裁一出<br />\n眾高登仔都為奧巴馬打飛機<br />\n美菲合作支爆開始<br />\n當年英美日菲澳基本所有盟一樣圍中國<br />\n結果填島無停過<br />\nD島仲愈填愈快 而家飛機防空導彈都係上面<br />\n而家班傻仔提都唔敢提南海仲裁單野<br />\n美國輸成點<br />\n所以貿易戰 連登仔愈興奮<br />\n我愈覺得中國反而愈唔死得<br />\n不服來辯<br />\n屌你老母連登仔 獨派<br />\n再多唔洗十年 中國全面接管香港<br />\n我會組織香港共青團<br />\n我就會帶隊清算你班社會垃圾"},{"pid":"3d4180cb2dbc95e10915e88e8677c438690bc66f","tid":1166351,"uid":98232,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"睇清形勢 及早埋中共堆<br />\n日後入黨做番一官半職都易d<br />\n帶無人跟隊"},{"pid":"db253d4d9d02f50bfe85eb7b10d1161022ba6814","tid":1166351,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505d56e0eac09e5d04020fea40ec745c684e7e43","tid":1166351,"uid":83251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b083dbc7edbf74b1b896f642d64d10750c4c13c","tid":1166351,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"505d56e0eac09e5d04020fea40ec745c684e7e43","tid":1166351,"uid":83251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:24:13.000Z","msg":"而家帶5蚊 我就黎上車買樓啦 柒頭"},{"pid":"d16839c5aa8a5c7fac1475ba62ff8f9910bceb67","tid":1166351,"uid":83251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1b083dbc7edbf74b1b896f642d64d10750c4c13c","tid":1166351,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote